		<div id="main">
				
			<h2><a href="web_dev.html">Want a Website?</a></h2>
			
			<p>Then you have come to the right place! I design websites for small businesses and for personal use.
			My websites are affordable yet are of professional quality. 
			</p>

			<h3>Types of Web Sites I Design</h3>
			<p>There are two main types of websites I can design, a site on <a href="http://sites.google.com/">Google Sites</a>
			or with a CSS template. There are advantages and disadvantages to both of the types of sites. 
			</p>
			
			<h4><a href="http://sites.google.com/">Google Sites</a></h4>

			<p>One advantage of <a href="http://sites.google.com/">Google Sites</a>
			 is that the web hosting and the domain name are totally free, so other than the inital cost of designing the site and whether or not 
			you would like a support package, there are no other costs. A disadvantage to <a href="http://sites.google.com/">Google Sites</a> 
			is that there are limited capabilities in what can go in the site and the over all desgining of the site. </p>

			<h4>CSS Template</h4>
			
			<p>One advantage of CSS templates is that the design possibilities are nearly endless. There are disadvantages
			to using a CSS template. When using a CSS template the customer has to buy their own domain name and pay for web hosting.
			Depending on the provider and the domain name these could get fairly costly.</p>

			<h3>Examples</h3>

			<p>Here are some examples of some websites that I have designed. </p> 

			<h4><a href="http://sites.google.com/">Google Sites</a></h4>

			<p>This is the first website I ever designed using the <a href="http://sites.google.com/">Google Sites</a> platform,
			<a href="https://sites.google.com/site/riverviewibsurvivalguide/">Riverview IB Survival-Guide</a>.
			
			<p>This is another one of my sites that I designed using the <a href="http://sites.google.com/">Google Sites</a> platform,
			<a href="https://sites.google.com/site/ramadawaterfrontsarasota/">Ramada Waterfront Sarasota</a>.
		
			<h4>CSS Templates</h4>

			<p>I designed the site that you are currently on from a CSS template. This was my first attempt at using a CSS
			template, so it can only get better from here!</p>

			<p>I also designed <a href="http://www.andylyman.com" title="andylyman.com">andylyman.com</a> from a CSS template. This is a great example of a possible theme
			for water oriented businesses/person.</p>

			<p>I have designed the website for <a href="Http://www.bigleaguebbq.com" title="Big League BBQ">Big League BBQ</a> from a CSS template. Be sure to check it out.</p>
			
			<h3>How can I get one?</h3>

			<p>If you would like me to design your site you can send me an email, <a href="mailto:colelyman@shortmail.com">colelyman@shortmail.com</a>,
			and you can have a free consultation.</p>

